{"tid":1744271,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［手足唔係condom］一人一po留言俾理大手足","createTime":"2019-11-21T15:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T16:18:14.000Z","uid":90073,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"1460182e9d3a9abff2fc10536bd5b7022cc95db5","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n我對唔住你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令你地仍然留左響poly出未到黎<br />\n但係我想講我無唔記得你地<br />\n呢個禮拜我都食唔安瞓唔落<br />\n每次聽到有手足成功走到<br />\n成個人好開心<br />\n但我好想你地割我<br />\n我無資格叫你做手足<br />\n你地一定要撐住呀<br />\n不過 就算你地頂唔住<br />\n我地都會明白 因為付出最多之一嘅你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74d8b03f348eff81c16385dfd6360cb6fdeac87","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f1e308883abe94d9ae8d0b05f0a2f8f74c1fd45","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb9ff3744b2707541ec4caaadb6a9bd7ea83d784","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"193af3212d3e9a6acda47be132ea4b6d43d483ad","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f8837536e0cda7ba21b1d014dd008d7ac945cb81","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6d81a9dc71202e7f5dc9965f9477ccf715b98b0","tid":1744271,"uid":306003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"理大手足撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff434b44f