ssets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bacb36c19852090d03598abdc7d2815f2a2623","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:13:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"630c7cd8a528fdc8f2ef520f2e2148b710eb08a1","tid":1744271,"uid":315153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:35:17.000Z","msg":"對唔住 好似做唔到咩實際野幫你地&hellip;<br />\n但我地無忘記過係入面既手足嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地真係好叻好勇敢<br />\n記得要食飯啊 著多件衫<br />\n你地做咩決定都絕對支持<br />\n最緊要個人無事"},{"pid":"182a60219138827556a27867ba209f40b7edb317","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59df26ee434d15ec3be3d4383e8b9ba27d02457f","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"21560132e6537a3becaf3c871231e151f507c589","tid":1744271,"uid":324134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1460182e9d3a9abff2fc10536bd5b7022cc95db5","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n我對唔住你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令你地仍然留左響poly出未到黎<br />\n但係我想講我無唔記得你地<br />\n呢個禮拜我都食唔安瞓唔落<br />\n每次聽到有手足成功走到<br />\n成個人好開心<br />\n但我好想你地割我<br />\n我無資格叫你做手足<br />\n你地一定要撐住呀<br />\n不過 就算你地頂唔住<br />\n我地都會明白 因為付出最多之一嘅你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒😢"},{"pid":"c395897f076d638b192ed77bd5f7f10770ecb1fe","tid":1744271,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"169c3d027a5f26732d25bf18d453182b7351f9b2","tid":1744271,"uid":43496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0